text: Fiães may refer to the following places in Portugal: *Fiães (Melgaço), a parish in the municipality of Melgaço *Fiães (Santa Maria da Feira), a parish in the municipality of Santa Maria da Feira *Fiães (Trancoso), a parish in the municipality of Trancoso *Fiães (Valpaços), a parish in the municipality of Valpaços *Fiães do Rio, a parish in the municipality of Montalegre ==Other== *Fiães Sport Clube, a sporting club played in the parish of Fiaes in the municipality of Santa Maria da Feira
title: Fiães
